OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,FA holidaymaker who contracted a deadly
OL,7,Fdisease while in Cuba has been given a
OL,8,Ffive-figure payout from travel company
OL,9,FTui.
OL,11,FGary Cushnie was six days into a dream
OL,12,Ftrip with partner, Julie, in June 2022
OL,13,Fwhen he fell ill.
OL,15,FThe 63-year-old, from Willerby, East
OL,16,FYorkshire, was later diagnosed with
OL,17,FLegionnaires' disease - often
OL,18,Ftransmitted through airborne water
OL,19,Fparticles from contaminated plumbing
OL,20,Fsystems.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,FMr Cushnie believes he breathed in the
OL,7,Finfected particles while showering in
OL,8,Fthe Iberostar Grand Packard Hotel in
OL,9,FHavana.
OL,11,FWithin days of arriving, he began
OL,12,Fsuffering from chest pains, shortness
OL,13,Fof breath, lack of appetite and
OL,14,Fextreme fatigue. He spent the second
OL,15,Fweek unable to leave the hotel.
OL,17,FAfter returning home, Mr Cushnie was
OL,18,Fstill too ill to drive home and ended
OL,19,Fup being taken to Hull Royal Infirmary
OL,20,Fby ambulance, where he stayed for a
OL,21,Fweek.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,FDoctors later diagnosed him with
OL,7,Fpneumonia and pleurisy, before blood
OL,8,Ftests confirmed the presence of
OL,9,FLegionnaires' disease which was
OL,10,Ftreated with antibiotics.
OL,12,FNow, nearly four years on, Mr
OL,13,FCushnie's holiday providers - Tui -
OL,14,Fhave settled out of court after his
OL,15,Fsolicitors argued they failed to
OL,16,Fensure basic hygiene at the hotel,
OL,17,Fputting him and other holidaymakers at
OL,18,Frisk.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,FIt follows 1,700 cases being brought
OL,7,Fagainst the package holiday firm from
OL,8,Fcustomers who caught Shigella while
OL,9,Fholidaying in Cape Verde.
OL,11,FOne of them, Nicky Morley, 55, from
OL,12,FDevon, says she has been left with
OL,13,Flong-term health complications after
OL,14,Fcatching the bacterial illness staying
OL,15,Fat the five-star Riu Palace Santa
OL,16,FMaria in May 2022.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar, Mr Cushnie
OL,7,Fsaid: "I woke up in the morning and I
OL,8,Fhad this terrible pain in my chest and
OL,9,Frib area. I thought I'd strained a
OL,10,Fmuscle or done something. Obviously
OL,11,Fnow we know it was the pneumonia and
OL,12,Fthe pleurisy starting to kick in."
OL,14,FMr Cushnie believes he caught the
OL,15,Finfection after grabbing a shower upon
OL,16,Farriving at the hotel, after looking
OL,17,Fback and remembering there were issues
OL,18,Fwith the water starting.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@bO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,F"I did something I never, ever do and
OL,7,Fstood underneath the shower and turned
OL,8,Fit on. It just coughed and spluttered.
OL,9,FLittle did I know at the time, the
OL,10,Fcoughing and spluttering was showering
OL,11,Fme in legionella."
OL,13,FLegionnaires' comes from legionella
OL,14,Fbacteria, which can cultivate in
OL,15,Fcontaminated water systems before
OL,16,Fbeing inhaled through microscopic mist
OL,17,Fparticles.
OL,19,FIf left untreated, it can result in
OL,20,Fmajor respiratory problems, organ
OL,21,Ffailure and, in 10% of cases, death.
OL,26,@sD@RO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,FMr Cushnie said: "All I would say is,
OL,7,Fwherever you go, when you go in and
OL,8,Fturn the taps on, exit the shower room
OL,9,Fjust for 30 seconds. Because if
OL,10,Fthere's anything in the water tank -
OL,11,Fyou don't know how long that room has
OL,12,Fbeen empty. That's when it's
OL,13,Fsusceptible to legionella."
OL,15,FTui initially denied responsibility
OL,16,Ffor the illness, but later agreed to a
OL,17,Ffive-figure out-of-court settlement.
OL,26,@nD@ROUuD@[O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,FAnne Thomson, an expert in holiday
OL,7,Finjury and illness cases at Hudgell
OL,8,FSolicitors who represented Mr Cushnie,
OL,9,Fsaid: "In cases like this, package
OL,10,Fholiday operators often deny that one
OL,11,Fof the hotels they use has been the
OL,12,Fsource of the infection, as
OL,13,Fholidaymakers have usually been out
OL,14,Fand about enjoying local restaurants,
OL,15,Fwhere of course they come into contact
OL,16,Fwith various water systems.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,F"It is why we request to see policy
OL,7,Fdocuments and records from the travel
OL,8,Foperators themselves, and from the
OL,9,Fhotels they send guests to, in terms
OL,10,Fof hygiene inspections and safety
OL,11,Fchecks, cleaning and maintenance
OL,12,Frecords, and records of any other
OL,13,Fincidents of illness, and in
OL,14,Fparticular, cases of Legionnaires'."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Tui said: "We are
OL,17,Fvery sorry to hear about Mr Cushnie's
OL,18,Fillness and appreciate how distressing
OL,19,Fthis must have been.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@dO]xD@^OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1776877554
OL,3,CHolidaymaker who caught Legionnaires'
OL,4,Cin Cuba gets five-figure payout
OL,6,F"As TUI no longer operates in Cuba and
OL,7,Fdid not have access to sufficient
OL,8,Fevidence, the matter was resolved by
OL,9,Fway of an outofcourt settlement,
OL,10,Fwithout any admission of liability."
